{{Quote|Looks to me like he wasn't just chewing the luna-weed!|[[Serji-X Arrogantus]], referring to the [[Old One]]|<ref name="Star Wars (1977) 10">[[Star Wars (1977) 10|''Star Wars'' (1977) 10]]</ref>}}
'''Luna-weed''' was a plant native to [[Aduba-3/Legends|Aduba-3]]. If chewed, it could produce delusional effects in the user. It gave rise to the phrase "chewing the luna-weed" when referring to someone who was acting crazy.

